</br>22 Now it came about at that time that A·bim´e·lech together with Phi´col the chief of his army said to Abraham: “God is with you in everything you are doing.
</br>23 So now swear to me here by God that you will not prove false to me and to my offspring and to my posterity; that, according to the loyal love with which I have dealt with you, you will deal with me and with the land in which you have been residing as an alien.”
</br>24 So Abraham said: “I shall swear.”
